(\frac{\sqrt2}{2}, \frac{\sqrt2}{2}, -c)
\left(1-\frac{\sqrt2}{2}\right)^2+\frac{1}{2}+4c^2
4c^2 = 1\!\frac{1}{2}-\left(1-\frac{\sqrt2}{2}\right)^2 = \sqrt{2}
c=\dfrac{\sqrt[4]{2}}{2}
